This project is dual-licensed under either of the following licenses at your option:

- Apache License, Version 2.0 (LICENSE-APACHE or http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)
- MIT license (LICENSE-MIT or http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

We recommend choosing the Apache License 2.0 for the following benefits:

1. Patent protection: It includes an explicit patent license from contributors
2. Clear contribution terms: Well-defined terms for project contributions
3. Corporate-friendly: Widely accepted in enterprise environments
4. Better compatibility: Compatible with most other open source licenses

本项目采用双重许可证，您可以选择使用以下任一许可证：

- Apache 许可证 2.0 版（LICENSE-APACHE 或 http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0）
- MIT 许可证（LICENSE-MIT 或 http://opensource.org/licenses/MIT）

我们推荐选择 Apache 许可证 2.0，因为它具有以下优势：

1. 专利保护：包含贡献者明确的专利许可
2. 明确的贡献条款：对项目贡献有明确的定义
3. 企业友好：在企业环境中被广泛接受
4. 更好的兼容性：与大多数其他开源许可证兼容

For detailed license terms, please refer to the respective license files in the project root directory.
具体许可条款请参见项目根目录中的相应许可证文件。
